00:23:34.696 --> 00:23:36.136
higher number of T cells?

399
00:23:37.216 --> 00:23:40.896
So our data suggests longer duration breastfeeding in total

400
00:23:40.996 --> 00:23:41.836
cumulative over.

401
00:23:42.186 --> 00:23:42.186
Okay.

402
00:23:42.196 --> 00:23:44.316
But of course, you can't breastfeed without pregnancy, right?

403
00:23:44.326 --> 00:23:44.326
Right.

404
00:23:44.356 --> 00:23:45.756
So it's quite hard to deconvolute.

405
00:23:45.766 --> 00:23:45.896
Yeah.

406
00:23:46.396 --> 00:23:46.596
Yes.

407
00:23:46.636 --> 00:23:46.976
Thank you.

408
00:23:48.716 --> 00:23:50.936
Thank you, Sharyn, for that great presentation.

409
00:23:51.756 --> 00:23:55.296
I was thinking that maybe lactation looks like a vaccination.

