00:23:59.356 --> 00:24:02.436
that potential vaccine, would you target the whole

412
00:24:02.776 --> 00:24:04.696
population or just triple-negative?

413
00:24:06.408 --> 00:24:10.228
Yes. So one potential translation is that if we

414
00:24:10.288 --> 00:24:13.828
could find the antigen, of course, that is a hard thing to do, you could

415
00:24:13.868 --> 00:24:17.468
potentially think of vaccine strategies similar, analogous to HPV

