424
00:24:42.668 --> 00:24:43.688
there's a lot more work to do.

425
00:24:44.168 --> 00:24:45.728
Any ideas on the antigen?

426
00:24:46.288 --> 00:24:49.828
We have ideas, but nothing proven as yet.

427
00:24:50.048 --> 00:24:50.368
Thank you.

