00:25:53.958 --> 00:25:53.958
Right

449
00:25:53.958 --> 00:25:55.728
... as well as the hormonal effects.

450
00:25:55.738 --> 00:25:58.878
So, I think it's very complicated, and obviously this evolved-

451
00:25:59.428 --> 00:26:00.828
Yeah

452
00:26:00.838 --> 00:26:03.348
... over to keep mothers alive. So I think it's probably going to be quite

