811
00:47:32.218 --> 00:47:34.738
pro-proliferative gene in these tumors.

812
00:47:36.258 --> 00:47:39.678
And I think broadly, the findings that I've shown you are consistent with what

813
00:47:39.718 --> 00:47:43.298
we've sort of known about Rb for a long time, but not fully understood, which

814
00:47:43.358 --> 00:47:47.198
is we've always thought of it as a protein that can both repress the cell

815
00:47:47.238 --> 00:47:50.958
cycle, but sort of enforce lineage identity, and that means for these tumors,

